creator: Sun Cabs Taxis
descriptionHtml:
HOW IT WORKS
1. Enter your destination
2. Book the right vehicle type based on your needs
3. Track your driver’s position
4. Pay the fare in the app

FEATURES
- Passwordless registration flow
- Set a default tip to apply on your bookings
- Get an ETA for your next booking
- Get an approximate idea of how much it will cost you with the fare estimator
- Book now or prebook a taxi up to 7 days in advance
- Hassle-free in-app payment
- See your driver and vehicle details
- Track your vehicle arrival on the map and rate your driver at the end of the trip
- Automatically get your receipt by email after each trip paid through the app
- Book with your business account and automate expenses
descriptionShort: Book a taxi in under 10 seconds with the Sun Cabs app
